A}}\n\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Women===\n*[[Volleyball at the 1984 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|1984]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Lang Ping]]|CHN}}\n*[[Volleyball at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|1988]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Cecilia Tait]]|PER}}\n*[[Volleyball at the 1992 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|1992]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Paula Weishoff]]|USA}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rio2016.fivb.com/en/news/olympic-countdown---barcelona-rocks-to-a?id=59080|title=News detail - Olympic Countdown - Barcelona rocks to a Latin American rhythm - FIVB - Olympic Games - Rio 2016|author=|date=|website=rio2016.fivb.com|accessdate=30 April 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Volleyball at the 1996 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|1996]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Cintha Boersma]]|NED}}\n*[[Volleyball at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2000]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Barbara Jeli\u0107-Ru\u017ei\u0107|Barbara Jeli\u0107]]|CRO}}\n*[[Volleyball at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2004]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Feng Kun]]|CHN}}\n*[[Volleyball at the 2008 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2008]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Paula Pequeno]]|BRA}}\n*[[Volleyball at the 2012 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2012]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Kim Yeon-koung]]|KOR}}\n*[[Volleyball at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2016]] \u2013 {{flagathlete|[[Zhu Ting (volleyball)|Zhu Ting]]|CHN}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/FIVBVolleyball/status/767215190484156416 |title=FIVB:#Rio2016 women's #Volleyball Dream Team |publisher=fivb.com |date=20 Aug 2016 |accessdate=20 Aug 2016}}</ref>\n\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Win-loss records==\n\n===Men's tournament===\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Team!!width=\"50px\"|Matches played!!width=50px|Wins!!width=50px|Losses!!width=70px|[[Winning percentage]]\n|-\n|align=left|{{vb|ALG}}||6||0||6||.000\n|-\n|align=left|{{vb|ARG}}||47||22||25||.468\n|-\n|ali