wards|date=August 16, 2017|work=The Streamy Awards|access-date=December 7, 2017|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Shorty Awards]]\n|YouTuber of the Year\n|{{nominated}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://shortyawards.com/archive/influencers/9th/youtuber|title=Past Winners & Nominees - The Shorty Awards|website=shortyawards.com|access-date=December 6, 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[South Asian Canadians in the Greater Toronto Area]]<!--Source: https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/diljit-dosanjh-and-youtuber-lilly-singh-bond-over-punjabi-roots-watch/story-rB45noeTfoBa6ap1KOe6oL.html -->\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{official website}}\n* {{IMDb name|6530360}}\n* [https://www.iisuperwomanii.co/ IISuperwomanII] channel website\n\n{{Streamy Awards Winners CSS}}\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Singh, Lilly}}\n[[Category:21st-century Canadian comedians]]\n[[Category:Canadian women comedians]]\n[[Category:LGBT comedians]]\n[[Category:LGBT YouTubers]]\n[[Category:Female YouTubers]]\n[[Category:Canadian Internet celebrities]]\n[[Category:Canadian YouTubers]]\n[[Category:Canadian actresses of Indian descent]]\n[[Category:Canadian people of Punjabi descent]]\n[[Category:Canadian people of Indian descent]]\n[[Category:People from Scarborough, Toronto]]\n[[Category:Video bloggers]]\n[[Category:Women video bloggers]]\n[[Category:York University alumni]]\n[[Category:Canadian Sikhs]]\n[[Category:Streamy Award winners]]\n[[Category:YouTube Diamond Play Button recipients]]\n[[Category:YouTube Gold Play Button recipients]]\n[[Category:Canadian expatriate actresses in the United States]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Toronto]]\n[[Category:Canadian emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:Women bloggers]]\n[[Category:LGBT entertainers from Canada]]\n[[Category:Canadian expatriates in the United States]]\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Bisexual actresses]]\n[[Category:American television 